title: AntiFreeze
description: AntiFreeze is UASUevents’ week-long winter tournament, held the first week back in the winter semester! Dating back to its snowy origins as a 1913 shovel showdown, now 40 teams of 8-12 players compete in 10 indoor and outdoor games for the ultimate prize: an all-expenses-paid ski trip to Jasper! With events like Amazing Race-style adventure, speed-eating contests, dance-offs, obstacle courses, and more, there’s something for everyone to enjoy! Open all University of Alberta students, so grab your squad and bring the heat!
